3. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper deals with power control in a system with multiple transmitters and one receiver, which is a topic of interest in systems and control. 
4. cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems) - The paper deals with multiple transmitters adapting their power level, which is a topic of interest in multi-agent systems. 
5. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper deals with power control in multiple access channels, which is a topic of interest in networking and internet architecture.
